an>孙中山先生跟虚云老和尚有过一番对话，<span class="_ _8"></span>我以前</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y110 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls15 ws0">看过冯冯写的《空虚的云》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls33">，是介绍虚老事迹的一本书。书</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y111 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">中就讲了，<span class="_ _8"></span>孙中山先生觉得，<span class="_ _8"></span>基督教与佛教在精神上是很接</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y13f ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">近的。<span class="_ _10"></span>虚云老和尚告诉他，<span class="_ _b"></span>佛教与基督教本是同源，<span class="_ _b"></span>耶稣 18</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y140 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">岁以后曾往印度研究佛教，<span class="_ _8"></span>跟马鸣菩萨的弟子学过法。<span class="_ _8"></span>在印</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
